\n\n
His approach to make reusable components, write cleaner code and finding ways to remove boilerplate code is really fantastic.
\n\n
He is an amazing asset for any team and company. I wish him all the very best for his future assignments.
`,
        name: 'Sanoj Kumar',
        job: 'Principal Software Architect',
        relation: "Ankush Reported to Sanoj at TCS",
        image: {
          src: 'public/recommendations/sanoj-kumar--linkedin-profile-pic.jpeg',
          alt: 'Sanoj Singh Picture',
        },
      },
      {
        testimonial: `Ankush has been exceptional throughout the Labor Cost Portal Project , understanding the macro and documenting all the key items and making sure all key aspects are covered in the new application logic. He is always open to take challenges and solves production issues in small span of time. He effectively communicates the changes to BRM.`,
        name: 'Soumya Biswas',
        job: 'Technical Architect',
        image: {
          src: 'public/recommendations/soumya-biswas-linkedin-profile-pic.jpeg',
          alt: 'Soumya Biswas Picture',
        },
      },
      {
        testimonial: `I had the pleasure of working with Ankush on a project where we utilized Java, Spring Boot, and Angular. Ankush was a quick learner and showed a great curiosity to understand the reasons behind things, which made him a valuable member of the team. His dedication and ability to learn new technologies quickly made a positive impact on the project. I would highly recommend Ankush as a skilled and motivated developer who is always eager to take on new challenges and deliver results.`,
        name: 'Umang Budhwar',
        job: 'Senior Software Engineer',
        relation: "Ankush and Umang worked on the same team",
        image: {
          src: 'public/recommendations/umang-budhwar-linkedin-profile-pic.jpeg',
          alt: 'Umang Budhwar Profile Picture',
        },
      },
      {
        testimonial: `Ankush is a highly enthusiastic, energetic and a fast learner.He has the capability to quickly grasp the necessary domain, technology and process knowledge to deliver the right product at the right time.He volunteers for many of the account level initiatives and brings out of the box ideas for better execution.`,
        name: 'Priya Jayachandran',
        job: 'Agile Coach @ UBS',
        image: {
          src: 'public/recommendations/priya-jayachandran-linkedin-profile-pic.jpeg',
          alt: 'Priya Jayachandran Image',
        },
      },
      {
        testimonial: `Ankush is very hard working and go-to person for technical stuffs. A very techno savvy person and a good coder indeed! He always come up with good solution. I had very good experience working with him past couple years !!`,
        name: 'Deepa Mandal',
        job: 'Program Manager at TCS',
        image: {
          src: 'public/recommendations/deepa-mandal-linkedin-profile-pic.jpeg',
          alt: 'Deepa Mandal',
        },
      },
      {
        testimonial: `Hi Ankush,Appreciate your work done for CSF Forms project! The pieces you worked here were critical and you delivered them well . Keep up the good work.Thanks,Ritu`,
        name: 'Rituparna Ghosh',
        job: 'BRM at TCS',
        image: {
          src: 'public/recommendations/woman-profile-pic.png',
          attribution: {
            url: "https://www.freepik.com/icon/woman_2922566#fromView=keyword&term=Female&page=1&position=3&uuid=889e96ee-a25b-4dfa-a349-7fe200c47923",
            text: "Icon by Vitaly Gorbachev"
          },
          alt: 'Alex Foster Image',
        },
      },
    ]}
  />

  <!-- CallToAction Widget *********** -->

  <CallToAction
    title="Let's create together"
    subtitle="Ready to transform your vision into captivating designs?"
    actions={[{
      variant:"primary",
      text: 'Hire me',
      href: '/',
    }]}
  />

</Layout>
